-286041621.text: "Expectedly, hepatic mRNA expression of Ikk2 and classical targets of NF-kB activation, namely IkBalpha, serum amyloid a1 (Saa1), intercellular adhesion molecule 1 (Icam1), Bcl-x, and Akt1 [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR] were all significantly higher in 12-week-old male Liv-Ikk2ca mice than wild-type littermates."
